text: Mohammad Reza Rezaei Kouchi (; born 23 September 1971) is an Iranian politician who represents Jahrom in the Islamic Consultative Assembly since 2008. He is the head of the civil commission of the parliament. ==References== == Other websites == *mohammad reza rezaei On Instagram Category:1971 births Category:Iranian politicians Category:Iranian Muslims Category:Living people
